# Markdown Documentation Location

All new markdown (`.md`) documentation files must be created inside the `docs/` folder.

## Path convention

- **✅ Correct**: `docs/my-feature.md`, `docs/CLUSTER_RBAC_SEEDING_PLAN.md`, `docs/README-setup.md`
- **❌ Incorrect**: `my-feature.md` (root), `deploy/README-seeder.md` (use `docs/` instead when creating new docs)

## When to apply

- Creating new documentation or README-style content
- Adding design docs, plans, or guides
- The root `README.md` is the exception for project overview
